textBox.richText: Between Thanksgiving and Sunday, we didn’t get any flakes. Saturday was day 2 of Devo Travel Team for Max with Coach Scott...Alli stayed home, and I went and worked on my moguls. They had C-lift and Sunnyside open...under C-lift was sketchy (Sleeper, Little Ten, Freeriders, and Phantom). Same for Sunnyside (Bluebell, Roundhouse, and Edelweiss). Got some good work in though...charts below. Oh, and the perfect wax test: see if you can make it from Super Gauge, down past Olympia and uphill to the top of Cheshire/Jabber without skating.
